trans-unit.source: Represents a single item of data extracted from a workflow and all its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje pojedynczy element danych wyodrębnionych z przepływu pracy i wszystkie skojarzone adnotacje.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches a track point, it sends a tracking record to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Kiedy infrastruktury śledzenie czasu wykonywania zgodny punktu ścieżki, wysyła do usługi śledzenia rekord śledzenia.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> may contain <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects that specify data to be extracted from the workflow and returned in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> or the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>Lub <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>może zawierać <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>lub <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>obiektów, które Określ dane, który zostanie wyodrębniony z przepływu pracy i zwracany w <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>lub <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: A TrackingDataItem represents a single item of this extracted data in either <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: TrackingDataItem reprezentuje jeden element tego wyodrębnione dane w <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>lub <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref> class.
Gets and sets the list of annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera i ustawia listę adnotacje skojarzone z wyodrębnione dane.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> can specify annotations to be sent with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>Lub <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>można określić adnotacje do wysłania z wyodrębnione dane.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: These are contained in the Annotations property.
trans-unit.target: Są one zawarte we właściwości adnotacji.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> that contains the annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> zawierający adnotacje skojarzone z wyodrębnione dane.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the extracted data associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera lub ustawia wyodrębnione dane skojarzone z <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Data contains the member data, specified by an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>, that was extracted from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Dane zawierają dane elementu członkowskiego, określony przez <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>lub <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>, który został wyodrębniony z wystąpieniem przepływu pracy.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that represents the extracted data.
Gets or sets the name of the property or field associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera lub ustawia nazwę właściwości lub pola skojarzone z wyodrębnione dane.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure supports data extraction on fields and properties of classes that inherit from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>; a member of such a field or property; and a single item of a field or a property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface, for example a single element in a collection.
trans-unit.target: Infrastruktura śledzenie czasu wykonywania obsługuje wyodrębniania danych na pola i właściwości klas, które dziedziczą z <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>; element członkowski takiego pola lub właściwości; i jeden element pola lub właściwości (lub członkiem albo) implementujący <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>interfejsu, na przykład jeden element w kolekcji.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>

trans-unit.source: FieldName contains the dot delineated name of the item extracted and is equivalent to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> depending on which type of extract specified the data contained by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>.
trans-unit.target: Nazwa pola zawiera nazwę nakreślono kropka elementów wyodrębnionego i stanowi odpowiednik <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>lub <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>w zależności od tego, jakiego typu wyodrębniania określone dane zawierają przez <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>

trans-unit.source: The dot delineated name of the property or field that was extracted.
trans-unit.target: Kropka nakreślono nazwa właściwości lub pola, który został wyodrębniony.
